580
00:32:15,072 --> 00:32:17,568
♪Silently watching from the window♪

581
00:32:17,568 --> 00:32:21,280
♪Always hoping the promise remains♪

582
00:32:21,280 --> 00:32:23,904
♪I wait silently♪

583
00:32:23,904 --> 00:32:27,552
♪Gentle breeze blows, roses bloom♪

584
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:30,816
♪Leaning on each other's shoulders♪

585
00:32:31,072 --> 00:32:34,528
