622
00:34:31,272 --> 00:34:36,072
♪In dreams, I still feel sorry for you♪

623
00:34:38,312 --> 00:34:43,319
♪I can't help missing you♪

624
00:34:44,328 --> 00:34:48,872
♪My life got dull without you♪

625
00:34:48,872 --> 00:34:52,257
